title: 后台时不时刷这个报错
author: Tommer
txt_content:
[20:04:34 WARN]: An exceptionCaught() event was fired, and it reached at the tail of the pipeline. It usually means the last handler in the pipeline did not handle the exception.
java.nio.channels.ClosedChannelException: null
        at io.netty.channel.AbstractChannel$AbstractUnsafe.write(...)(Unknown Source) ~[spigot-1.12.2-R0.1-SNAPSHOT-b1648.jar:git-Spigot-642f6d2-57ab4cf]

replies.author: 十年后？
replies.txt_content: 无大碍的可以直接无视的 亲
可能是楼主的服务端版本问题，这种垃圾信息可以无视，如果您可以进入服务器无视就好了，如果楼主很想解决的话换个Spigot版本试一下。
